Task List E048_1

Objective:
Cofigure and HTTP server

Alex wants to install the Apache HTTP server package on a Rocky Linux system
which is similar to a Red Hat Enterprise Linux system.
What command will he use?
sudo dnf install httpd

Where does the HTTP server configuration file reside on RHEL-compatible systems?
/etc/httpd/conf/httpd.conf

Joanne wants to define server 192.168.1.1 in the httpd.conf file.
She opens the httpd.conf file using nano.
What line will she enter?
ServerName 192.168.1.1:80

Oscar wants to start the Apache HTTP server, and configure it to start after a system reboot.
What 2 commands will he run?
service http start
chkconfig httpd on

Oscar now wants to enable HTTP connection requests on port 80 through his firewall.
What commands will he run?
iptables -I INPUT -p tcp -m state --state NEW -m tcp --dport 80 -j ACCEPT
service iptables save





